{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/absurd/nightlight/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"fridge notes"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"6787ccbe-31b3-5e8e-9bbf-9338a5c9a573","excerpt":"From A Concept After a tumultuous ideation process, Philip and I have finally created a product we are proud of. Our initial idea was to create a solitary…","html":"<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/blog/static/c260634535e026fdbb89f3f43a614e38/81e52/3Quater.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 66.89189189189189%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"our final product, an adult nightlight that tells you generated bedtime stories so that you don&#39;t have to go to a bar yourself\"\n        title=\"our final product, an adult nightlight that tells you generated bedtime stories so that you don&#39;t have to go to a bar yourself\"\n        src=\"/blog/static/c260634535e026fdbb89f3f43a614e38/fcda8/3Quater.png\"\n        srcset=\"/blog/static/c260634535e026fdbb89f3f43a614e38/12f09/3Quater.png 148w,\n/blog/static/c260634535e026fdbb89f3f43a614e38/e4a3f/3Quater.png 295w,\n/blog/static/c260634535e026fdbb89f3f43a614e38/fcda8/3Quater.png 590w,\n/blog/static/c260634535e026fdbb89f3f43a614e38/efc66/3Quater.png 885w,\n/blog/static/c260634535e026fdbb89f3f43a614e38/c83ae/3Quater.png 1180w,\n/blog/static/c260634535e026fdbb89f3f43a614e38/81e52/3Quater.png 4075w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">our final product, an adult nightlight that tells you generated bedtime stories so that you don&#39;t have to go to a bar yourself</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<h2>From A Concept</h2>\n<p>After a tumultuous ideation process, Philip and I have finally created a product we are proud of. Our initial idea was to create a solitary drinking experience, which then evolved into a multi-person drinking experience. We wanted to enhance the intimacy of being in a bar, which is already an inherently intimate setting. The problem we kept running into was trying to gamify it, which does not necessarily imply an absurd design. We focused too much on the way to achieve the feeling of being connected with another person. </p>\n<p>However.</p>\n<p>If we flipped that idea around, what if we removed the other person from the picture?</p>\n<p>What if we removed the <em>whole bar</em> from a design intended to augment the bar experience?</p>\n<p>What if we brought the bar experience <em>to you</em>?</p>\n<p>What if you didn’t want to go out, but still felt obligated to tell your friends you did?</p>\n<p>So, how can we create the bar experience from your own bed?</p>\n<p>Introducing…</p>\n<p>The Adult NightLight™️</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/blog/static/e6fb14e432e119b5bba45e3e82c71b64/df3a3/Ortho.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 66.89189189189189%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Ortho\"\n        title=\"Ortho\"\n        src=\"/blog/static/e6fb14e432e119b5bba45e3e82c71b64/fcda8/Ortho.png\"\n        srcset=\"/blog/static/e6fb14e432e119b5bba45e3e82c71b64/12f09/Ortho.png 148w,\n/blog/static/e6fb14e432e119b5bba45e3e82c71b64/e4a3f/Ortho.png 295w,\n/blog/static/e6fb14e432e119b5bba45e3e82c71b64/fcda8/Ortho.png 590w,\n/blog/static/e6fb14e432e119b5bba45e3e82c71b64/efc66/Ortho.png 885w,\n/blog/static/e6fb14e432e119b5bba45e3e82c71b64/c83ae/Ortho.png 1180w,\n/blog/static/e6fb14e432e119b5bba45e3e82c71b64/df3a3/Ortho.png 4792w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span><br>\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/blog/static/a66bbe1c9fce2dfff26f2f4eba0e91f6/007b1/Side.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 66.89189189189189%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Side\"\n        title=\"Side\"\n        src=\"/blog/static/a66bbe1c9fce2dfff26f2f4eba0e91f6/fcda8/Side.png\"\n        srcset=\"/blog/static/a66bbe1c9fce2dfff26f2f4eba0e91f6/12f09/Side.png 148w,\n/blog/static/a66bbe1c9fce2dfff26f2f4eba0e91f6/e4a3f/Side.png 295w,\n/blog/static/a66bbe1c9fce2dfff26f2f4eba0e91f6/fcda8/Side.png 590w,\n/blog/static/a66bbe1c9fce2dfff26f2f4eba0e91f6/efc66/Side.png 885w,\n/blog/static/a66bbe1c9fce2dfff26f2f4eba0e91f6/c83ae/Side.png 1180w,\n/blog/static/a66bbe1c9fce2dfff26f2f4eba0e91f6/007b1/Side.png 4878w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span>\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/blog/static/dd740ab759a9cca7bbc64eb4a6296df1/91306/Front.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 66.89189189189189%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Front\"\n        title=\"Front\"\n        src=\"/blog/static/dd740ab759a9cca7bbc64eb4a6296df1/fcda8/Front.png\"\n        srcset=\"/blog/static/dd740ab759a9cca7bbc64eb4a6296df1/12f09/Front.png 148w,\n/blog/static/dd740ab759a9cca7bbc64eb4a6296df1/e4a3f/Front.png 295w,\n/blog/static/dd740ab759a9cca7bbc64eb4a6296df1/fcda8/Front.png 590w,\n/blog/static/dd740ab759a9cca7bbc64eb4a6296df1/efc66/Front.png 885w,\n/blog/static/dd740ab759a9cca7bbc64eb4a6296df1/c83ae/Front.png 1180w,\n/blog/static/dd740ab759a9cca7bbc64eb4a6296df1/91306/Front.png 3120w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p><div class=\"gatsby-resp-iframe-wrapper\" style=\"padding-bottom: 50%; position: relative; height: 0; overflow: hidden; \" > <div class=\"embedVideo-container\"> <iframe title src=\"https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/t8E7uKg4IqM?rel=0\" class=\"embedVideo-iframe\" style=\"border:0; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; \" allowfullscreen></iframe> </div> </div></p>\n<h2>Software</h2>\n<h1>Generated Stories</h1>\n<p>The first part of the software process was generating the stories, which means finding a corpus. Reddit is a great place to find user submitted stories, and I ended up using the <a href=\"https://www.npmjs.com/package/snoowrap\">snoowrap api</a>.</p>\n<p>From there, it was a matter of picking the thread (which ended up being pulled from r/AskReddit) and pulling the top level comments. We pulled about 500 separate stories to use as our corpus for our generation script.</p>\n<p>After that, we used a markov chain (to see what <em>these</em> do, check out the wiki page), and this specific <a href=\"https://github.com/Edwin-Pratt/js-markov\">javascript library</a> implementation.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/samheckle/nightlight/blob/main/script.js\">final generation code</a></p>\n<h1>Processing</h1>\n<p>Processing was a bit more difficult than the story generation. We started with the animation  </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/samheckle/nightlight/blob/main/nightlight.pde\">final processing code</a></p>\n<h1>Previous iteration blog posts for this project:</h1>\n<p><a href=\"https://cadoux-itp.notion.site/Fall-2021-Blog-2f87c6bb054f45f1aeebeb3dbcb873ca?p=06156af79a724b2fa10eff72523630da\">first ideation</a>\n<a href=\"http://samheckle.com/blog/absurd/assignment-3/\">second ideation</a></p>","frontmatter":{"title":"Bedside Bartender: An Adult Nightlight","date":"November 11, 2021","description":"Documentation for our Adult Nightlight, a nightlight that tells you generated bedtime stories so that you don't have to go to the bar yourself."}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/absurd/nightlight/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/thesis/blog1/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Ideation 1"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/biomaterials/week-3/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Week 3 Assignments"}}}},"staticQueryHashes":["2841359383","3257411868"]}